'''ᱢᱟᱞᱚᱵᱷᱤᱠᱟ ᱥᱚᱨᱩᱠᱠᱟᱭ''' ᱢᱤᱫ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱮᱱᱮᱡᱤᱜ ᱟᱨ ᱵᱷᱟᱨᱚᱛᱱᱟᱴᱭᱚᱢ ᱨᱮ ᱯᱟᱹᱨᱩᱠᱷᱩᱭᱟᱹ ᱤᱡ ᱠᱚᱨᱤᱭᱚᱜᱨᱟᱯᱷᱚᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾<ref name="INK Talks">{{cite web | url=http://www.inktalks.com/people/malavikasarukkai | title=INK Talks | publisher=INK Talks | date=2015 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref><ref name="Kennedy Center">{{cite web | url=https://www.kennedy-center.org/explorer/artists/?entity_id=62204&source_type=A## | title=Kennedy Center | publisher=Kennedy Center | date=2015 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref><ref name="Walk The Talk with Malavika Sarukkai">{{cite web | url=http://www.ndtv.com/video/player/walk-the-talk/walk-the-talk-with-malavika-sarukkai-aired-february-2006/294826 | title=Walk The Talk with Malavika Sarukkai | publisher=[[NDTV]] | date=February 2006 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref> ᱟᱡ ᱟᱭᱳ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢ ᱥᱟᱨᱚᱡᱟ ᱠᱟᱢᱟᱠᱥᱤ ᱥᱟᱨᱩᱠᱠᱟᱭ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾ <ref  name="Malavika Sarukkai
">https://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/dance/malavika-sarukkai-plays-arjuna-and-krishna-in-her-forthcoming-production/article29776888.ece</ref> ᱩᱱᱤᱫᱚ ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱮᱱᱮᱡ ᱰᱷᱟᱝ ᱤᱫᱤ ᱛᱮ ᱩᱱᱤᱭᱟᱜ ᱤᱠᱥᱤᱴᱢᱮᱸᱴ (excitement) ᱫᱚ ᱩᱱᱤ ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱮᱱᱮᱡ ᱪᱮᱫᱚᱜ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱛᱮ ᱤᱱᱥᱯᱭᱟᱨ (Inspire) ᱠᱮᱫᱟ ᱵᱷᱟᱨᱚᱛᱱᱟᱴᱭᱚᱢ ᱪᱮᱫᱚᱜ ᱮᱦᱚᱵᱽ ᱠᱮᱫᱼᱟ ᱩᱱᱤ ᱾ [[ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱥᱚᱨᱠᱟᱨ]] ᱤᱫᱤ ᱛᱮ ᱨᱟᱦᱟ ᱟᱲᱟᱝ ᱜᱟᱭᱟᱱ ᱮᱠᱮᱰᱮᱢᱤ ᱥᱤᱨᱯᱷᱟᱹ ᱮᱢᱟᱫ ᱫᱮᱭᱟ ᱠᱚ,
<ref name="Sangeet Natak AKademi Award">{{cite web|url=http://sangeetnatak.gov.in/sna/awardeeslist.htm |title=Sangeet Natak AKademi Award |publisher=Sangeet Natak AKademi |date=2015 |accessdate=8 February 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530204253/http://sangeetnatak.gov.in/sna/awardeeslist.htm |archivedate=30 May 2015 }}</ref> ᱟᱨ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱥᱚᱨᱠᱟᱨ ᱤᱫᱤ ᱛᱮ ᱒᱐᱐᱓ ᱨᱮ ᱯᱩᱱᱭᱟ ᱩᱥᱩᱞ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱥᱟᱦᱨᱤ ᱯᱟᱫᱢᱟ ᱥᱨᱤ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱦᱚᱸ ᱢᱟᱱ ᱪᱟᱞ ᱟᱫᱮᱭᱟ ᱠᱚ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾  <ref name="Padma Awards">{{cite web|url=http://mha.nic.in/sites/upload_files/mha/files/LST-PDAWD-2013.pdf |title=Padma Awards |publisher=Padma Awards |date=2015 |accessdate=6 February 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6U68ulwpb?url=http://mha.nic.in/sites/upload_files/mha/files/LST-PDAWD-2013.pdf |archivedate=15 November 2014 }}</ref> ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱮᱱᱮᱡ ᱟᱨ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱟᱜ ᱞᱟᱹᱠᱛᱤᱭᱟᱱ ᱞᱟᱠᱪᱟᱨ ᱨᱮ Excellence ᱫᱚ ᱵᱟᱲᱦᱟᱣ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱛᱮ, ᱢᱟᱞᱚᱵᱷᱤᱠᱟ ᱫᱚ ᱠᱟᱞᱟᱵᱷᱤᱱᱤ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱯᱟᱹᱛᱭᱟᱹᱣ ᱵᱮᱱᱟᱣ ᱮᱱᱟ, ᱚᱠᱚᱭᱟᱜ ᱵᱷᱚᱨᱥᱟ ᱮᱢᱚᱜᱤᱦ ᱮᱱᱮᱡᱤᱜ ᱟᱜ ᱫᱚᱨᱥᱟᱨ ᱯᱤᱲᱤ ᱟᱜ ᱴᱷᱤᱠᱟᱹ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱛᱮ ᱟᱨ ᱩᱱᱤᱭᱟᱜ ᱯᱨᱩᱥᱴᱩᱠᱚᱨ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ, ᱱᱚᱣᱟ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱡᱩᱫᱟᱹ ᱮᱱᱮᱡ ᱫᱮᱠᱷᱟᱣ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱜᱩᱬ ᱞᱟᱦᱟᱭ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱛᱮ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾<ref>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/kolkata/cultural-evening-on-bharatanatyam-to-take-place-in-kolkata/articleshow/74304580.cms</ref>

==ᱡᱤᱭᱚᱱ==
ᱢᱟᱞᱚᱵᱷᱤᱠᱟ ᱥᱟᱨᱩᱠᱠᱟᱭ ᱟᱜ ᱡᱟᱱᱟᱢ ᱑᱙᱕᱙ ᱨᱮ ᱮᱛᱚᱢ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱯᱚᱱᱚᱛ [[ᱛᱟᱢᱤᱞᱱᱟᱰᱩ]] ᱨᱮ ᱦᱩᱭ ᱞᱮᱱᱟ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾ <ref name="Historical dictionary of the Tamils">{{cite book | url=http://www.worldcat.org/search?q=9780810853799&qt=owc_search | title=Historical dictionary of the Tamils | publisher=Lanham, Md. : Scarecrow Press | author=Vijaya Ramaswamy | year=2007 | isbn=9780810853799}}</ref> ᱩᱱᱤᱫᱚ ᱗ ᱥᱟᱞ ᱩᱢᱚᱨ ᱨᱮ ᱵᱷᱟᱨᱚᱛᱱᱟᱴᱭᱚᱢ ᱪᱮᱫᱚᱜ ᱮᱦᱚᱵᱽ ᱞᱮᱫᱼᱟ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱟᱨ [[ᱠᱟᱞᱭᱟᱬᱥᱩᱱᱫᱚᱨᱚᱢ ᱯᱤᱞᱞᱟᱭ]] (ᱛᱟᱝᱡᱟᱯᱩᱨ ᱟᱥᱲᱟ) ᱟᱨ [[ᱨᱟᱡᱟᱨᱚᱛᱱᱚᱢ]] (ᱵᱟᱡᱷᱩᱵᱩᱨ ᱟᱥᱲᱟ) ᱨᱮ ᱥᱮᱪᱮᱫᱚᱜ ᱞᱮᱱᱟ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾ <ref name="Indian Arts">{{cite web | url=http://www.indiansarts.com/malavikapage.htm | title=Indian Arts | publisher=Indian Arts | date=2015 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref><ref name="Bengal Foundation">{{cite web | url=http://www.bengalfoundation.org/?post_type=singer&p=33886 | title=Bengal Foundation | publisher=Bengal Foundation | date=2015 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref><ref name="Interview">{{cite interview | title=Interview | date=2015 | accessdate=8 February 2015 | last=Malavika Sarukkai | interviewer=Veejay Sai | URL=http://www.artindia.net/veejay9.html}}</ref> ᱩᱱᱤᱫᱚ [[ᱠᱟᱞᱟᱱᱤᱫᱷᱤ ᱱᱟᱨᱟᱭᱚᱬᱚᱱ]] ᱟᱜ ᱛᱟᱹᱨᱤ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱪᱮᱫ ᱠᱮᱫᱼᱟ ᱟᱨ ᱩᱱᱤᱫᱚ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢᱟᱱ ᱜᱩᱨᱩ, [[ᱠᱮᱞᱩᱪᱚᱨᱚᱬ ᱢᱚᱦᱟᱯᱟᱛᱨᱚ]] ᱟᱨ [[ᱨᱚᱢᱬᱤ ᱨᱟᱝᱡᱚᱱ ᱡᱮᱱᱟ]] ᱟᱜ ᱞᱮᱠᱟ [[ᱳᱰᱤᱥᱤ]] ᱦᱚᱸ ᱪᱮᱫ ᱠᱮᱫᱼᱟ ᱾ <ref name="Indian Arts" /><ref name="Bengal Foundation" /><ref name="Interview" /> ᱩᱱᱤᱫᱚ ᱑᱒ ᱥᱟᱞ ᱩᱢᱚᱨ ᱨᱮ [[ᱢᱩᱢᱵᱟᱭ]]  <ref name="Indian Arts" /><ref name="Blouin Art Info">{{cite web | url=http://in.blouinartinfo.com/news/story/958960/dancer-malavika-sarukkai-in-the-unseen-sequence | title=Blouin Art Info | publisher=Blouin Art Info | date=2015 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref> ᱨᱮ ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱮᱛᱚᱦᱚᱵ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱟᱨ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱥᱟᱶᱛᱮ ᱵᱤᱫᱮᱥ ᱨᱮ ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱜᱟᱱ ᱛᱷᱟᱱ ᱨᱮ ᱫᱮᱠᱷᱟᱣ ᱟᱠᱟᱫᱼᱟ ᱾ <ref name="Malavika Sarukkai: A tribute to Thimmakka">{{cite web | url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iIfmI27Nh_Q | title=Malavika Sarukkai: A tribute to Thimmakka | publisher=INKTalks | date=13 November 2013 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref><ref name="Padmashri Malavika Sarukkai Performs Bharatanatyam - Yaksha 2014">{{cite web | url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FCqj77FcSLU | title=Padmashri Malavika Sarukkai Performs Bharatanatyam - Yaksha 2014 | publisher=Isha Foundation | date=21 February 2014 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref><ref name="Canary Promo">{{cite web | url=http://www.canarypromo.com/pressrelease/MalavikaSarukkai | title=Canary Promo | publisher=Canary Promo | date=2015 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref><ref name="TOI India performance">{{cite web | url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chennai/Dance-has-been-my-life-since-I-was-7-Malavika-Sarukkai/articleshow/14422225.cms | title=TOI India performance | publisher=TOI | date=27 June 2012 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref> ᱚᱠᱟ ᱨᱮ, [[ᱞᱤᱸᱠᱟᱱ ᱥᱮᱱᱴᱟᱨ ᱯᱷᱳᱨ ᱫᱟ ᱯᱟᱨᱯᱷᱳᱨᱢᱤᱝ ᱟᱨᱴᱥ]], [[ᱱᱤᱭᱩ ᱭᱚᱨᱠ]], <ref name="Huffington Post">{{cite web | url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/ramaa-reddy-raghavan/malavika-sarukkai-achievi_b_4486246.html | title=Huffington Post | publisher=Huffington Post | date=21 December 2013 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref> [[ᱡᱳᱱ ᱮᱯᱷ ᱠᱮᱱᱮᱰᱤ ᱥᱮᱱᱴᱟᱨ ᱯᱷᱳᱨ ᱫᱟ ᱯᱟᱨᱯᱷᱳᱨᱢᱤᱝ ᱟᱨᱴᱥ]]  <ref name="New York Times">{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/11/19/arts/dance/malavika-sarukkai-at-the-baryshnikov-arts-center.html?_r=0 | title=Stories Told With a Leap, Even a Shake | newspaper=New York Times | date=18 November 2012 | first=Brian | last=Seibert | accessdate=18 May 2017}}</ref>  [[ᱥᱤᱠᱟᱜᱚ]] ᱨᱮ।<ref name="Pulse Connects">{{cite web | url=http://www.pulseconnects.com/content/ConversationMalavikaSarukkai | title=Pulse Connects | publisher=Pulse Connects | date=2015 | accessdate=8 February 2015}}</ref> ᱩᱱᱤᱭᱟᱜ ᱡᱤᱭᱚᱱ ᱟᱨ ᱠᱟᱹᱢᱤ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱥᱚᱨᱠᱟᱨ ᱤᱫᱤ ᱛᱮ ᱱᱩᱛᱷᱤ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ, '''ᱥᱚᱢᱚᱨᱯᱟᱱᱟᱢ''' ᱛᱟᱞᱟ ᱛᱮ ᱦᱩᱭ ᱟᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾  <ref name="Indian Arts" /><ref name="Bengal Foundation" /><ref name="Canary Promo" />ᱩᱱᱤᱫᱚ '''ᱮᱱᱮᱡ''' ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱛᱟᱹᱨᱤ ᱵᱤᱵᱤᱥᱤ/WNET ᱤᱫᱤ ᱛᱮ ᱟᱨᱮ ᱴᱟᱲᱟᱝ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱴᱮᱞᱤᱵᱤᱡᱟᱱ ᱱᱩᱛᱷᱤ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱨᱮ ᱦᱚᱸ ᱥᱮᱱ ᱮᱱᱟ,  <ref name="Indian Arts" /><ref name="Bengal Foundation" /><ref name="Blouin Art Info" /> '''ᱫᱟ ᱟᱱᱥᱤᱱ ᱥᱤᱠᱣᱮᱸᱥ ᱼ ᱮᱠᱥᱯᱞᱚᱨᱤᱝ ᱵᱷᱟᱨᱚᱛᱱᱟᱴᱭᱚᱢ ᱛᱷᱟᱨᱩ ᱫᱟ ᱟᱨᱴ ᱳᱯᱷ ᱢᱟᱞᱚᱵᱷᱤᱠᱟ ᱥᱟᱨᱩᱠᱠᱟᱭ''' ᱩᱱᱤᱫᱚ ᱵᱟᱰᱚᱦᱤ ᱨᱮ ᱵᱮᱱᱟᱣ ᱮᱱᱟ ᱟᱨ ᱚᱱᱚᱞ ᱯᱷᱤᱞᱢ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱚᱠᱚᱭ ᱢᱩᱢᱵᱟᱭ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱱᱮᱥᱱᱟᱞ ᱥᱮᱱᱴᱟᱨ ᱯᱷᱳᱨ ᱫᱟ ᱟᱨᱴᱥ ᱨᱮ ᱫᱮᱠᱷᱟᱣ ᱠᱮᱫᱼᱟ ᱾ । <ref name="Blouin Art Info" />
